short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Enter a product number.  New tabs open with info about this part, cross references, E2E forum discussions.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Enter a Product Number and quickly open 4 new tabs:

Product Page - Enter a generic product number (the name at the top of the product page) for this to work, eg. OPA192.

Cross reference search - Find alternate parts from TI.

E2E forum search - Search the support forum.

Search ti.com - Search the whole site for this Product Number.

TI uses Generic Product Numbers (eg. OPA192) and Orderable Part Numbers (eg. OPA192DBVR). This Add-on works best if you enter the Generic Product Number, but it will work with either.

Not officially supported by TI.
